{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_10_03",
  "title": "成宮すず 3話 何にもかえがたい喜び",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――新曲MV撮影の現場にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the set of the new song MV shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_photo_studio-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 1.8533333492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "この曲に合った表情やポーズ……ですか\n分かりましたわ。それではこういった感じはいかが？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean expressions and poses that suit this song?\nI understand. Well then‚ how about something like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ったら、戻って来たと思えばすぐに目覚ましい）\n（活躍をして……やはりあなたは、凄いですわね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono‚ ever since she returned‚ has been giving）\n（impressive performances… she really is amazing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "（ですが、私も負けるつもりはさらさらありませんから）\n（油断していたらいつでもセンターの座を奪いますわよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（However‚ I have no intention of losing either.）\n（I'll take the center position anytime if you let your guard down.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（すず……力強くて、それでいて優しい表情をしてる）\n（こんな顔をするようになったんだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Suzu… she has a strong‚ yet kind expression.）\n（She can make expressions like that now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "（これからは、私が今までの何倍も、何十倍も）\n（しっかりと月ストを支えてみせますわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（From now on‚ I'm going to support Moon Tempest many times‚）\n（dozens of times‚ more than I have ever before.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "（あなたが照らしてくれたように。私も、あなたを）\n（照らします。もう、一人で迷わないように）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Just like you shone on me‚ I‚ too‚ will shine on you.）\n（so you don't get lost on your own again.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "（私達五人の月のテンペストで）\n（アイドルの頂点に輝きますわよ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（With the five of us‚ Moon Tempest‚）\n（we'll shine at the top of the idol world!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影から数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after the MV shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3666707629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 69.5333407629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n今度の単独ライブでのセンターについてですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.\nAbout the center position at the upcoming solo live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "練習で私と琴乃がそれぞれセンターに立った時の\n手応えを比べた上で、メンバーで話し合いをしましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We compared how it felt when Kotono and I each stood\nin the center during practice‚ and we talked it over with the members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "結果はどうだったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What was the result?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1666722933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "センターは、どちらか一方が務めるのではなく\n曲ごとに切り替えることにしましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The center position will not be held by just one of us‚\nbut we decided to switch it up for each song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そしてその結果……この間話していた曲のセンターは\nこの私が務めることになりましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… for the center of the song we talked about the other day‚\nI will be the one taking the center position!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふーん。やはり私こそが\nあの曲のセンターにふさわしいんですのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoho-. After all‚ I'm the one\nwho's most suited to be the center for that song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな納得した上で、すずが人一倍思い入れのある曲の\nセンターになれて良かったよ。おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since everyone agreed‚ I'm glad you could take the center for the song\nthat means the most to you‚ Suzu. Congratulations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "後はもう、単独ライブに向けてステージングを\nひたすら詰めていくだけですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All that's left is to keep working on the staging for the solo live.\nI'm just going to keep working on it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4286859194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家の親族一同も感動でむせび泣くパフォーマンスを\n見せて差し上げますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll show all the Narumiya family relatives a performance\nthat will make them sob with emotion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月スト単独ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the Day of Moon Tempest's Solo Live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.073543167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 131.4000007629
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 131.4000007629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、私達月ストの単独ライブ……\n楽しんでいますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ how is Moon Tempest's solo live…?\nAre you enjoying it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7000007629,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.645526899993,
          "startTime": 137.8333340962
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます\nみなさんの熱気がこちらまで伝わってきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you.\nI can feel everyone's enthusiasm all the way over here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3999946593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 146.4333491324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "さて、次の曲なんですが\nこの曲は琴乃が月ストを離れていた頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ for the next song‚\nThis next song is one we made while Kotono was away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.366661326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 154.5666824657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "……私達が四人体制の時に作った曲ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…During the time we were a four-member group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5666824657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 158.7666824657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "もう、琴乃ったら。そんな神妙な面持ちにならないで\nくださいまし。どーんと構えていなさい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Kotono. Don't make such a solemn face.\nJust be confident and composed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0999946593,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.318297199986,
          "startTime": 166.0000007629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 167.0666794139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "四人で新曲を作るとなった時、初めは難航しましたわ\nいろいろなことがあり過ぎて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we decided to make a new song with the four of us‚ it was difficult at first.\nToo many things had happened‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4999916075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろな想いが溢れ過ぎて……\n気持ちが、言葉が、まとまりませんでしたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and too many feelings were overflowing…\nSo‚ we couldn't organize our feelings and words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.4275637625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 183.2000127473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達が今一番考えていることは何か……\nと考えたら、答えは一つでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ when we thought about what what was really on our minds…\nThere was only one answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9999916075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "テーマが決まればとんとん拍子で、曲が完成するまで\nあまりに早くて、思わず笑ってしまいましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once the theme was decided‚ everything flowed so smoothly that the song\ncame together in no time— I couldn't help but laugh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.4999966937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
