      "text": "（すずのMCにみんなが引き込まれてる）\n（ファンも気になっていた話題なんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone's being drawn in by Suzu's MC.）\n（It's probably a topic that the fans were curious about too.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.466673533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
