      "text": "初めてこの曲を披露した時、私達は\n「この想いが届けばいいな」と願って歌いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we performed this song for the first time‚ we\nsang with the wish that \"We want to deliver these feelings to you.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.1999966937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
