      "text": "結果として、月ストは五人に戻ることが出来て\nBIG4にもなれましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a result‚ Moon Tempest was able to return to being five people‚\nand we were also able to become BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.1666633604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
