      "text": "私達四人の、琴乃への想いが届いたことが……\n何にもかえがたい喜びなのだと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fact that the four of us were able to reach Kotono with our feelings…\nis a joy nothing else can replace.",
        "id": ""
